   Griffin, A. Rod; Hingston, Andrew B., Univ Tasmania, Sch Plant Sci, Hobart, Tas 7001, Australia.
   Griffin, A. Rod; Hingston, Andrew B., Univ Tasmania, CRC Forestry, Hobart, Tas 7001, Australia.
   Hingston, Andrew B., Univ Tasmania, Sch Geog \& Environm Studies, Hobart, Tas 7001, Australia.
   Ohmart, Clifford P., Lodi Winegrape Commiss, Lodi, CA 95242 USA.},
